¶ this.boundedBuffer = new ArrayBlockingQueue<>(this.BUFFER_SIZE); ¶ } ¶ ¶ public String getInputString() { ¶ return this.inputString; ¶ } ¶ ¶ public void clearReductionQueues() { ¶ for (ConcurrentLinkedQueue<KeyValue<String, Integer>> reductionQueue: reductionQueueList) { ¶ reductionQueue.clear(); ¶ this.pcs.firePropertyChange(updateInputStringEvent); ¶ } ¶ ¶ public void initializeStructures() { ¶ this.result = new HashMap<>(); ¶ this.boundedBuffer = new ArrayBlockingQueue<>(this.BUFFER_SIZE);
